                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18030914-34-off205 t18030914-34-cd206"></join>, two pair of stocking, value 4s. three shirts, value 12s. two shifts, value 1s. and a child's frock, value 6d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18030914-34-victim325" type="victimName">
                     James 
